sub_title: Natural Language Processing Enthusiast | Data Scientist at Underlined | Women in AI
summary:
Started with a passion for language and linguistics which first led to a focus on PR and communications. Then I discovered the fascinating world of Natural Language Processing and have been enchanted by it ever since. Currently, I am working as a medior data scientist focusing on tasks like Topic Modeling and Sentiment Analysis. 

I am also part of the Dutch AI Ethics Community and a mentee of the WomenInAI Netherlands mentorship program.
